EASEL ON


             Cash Reward Balance Option - Help

    Balance option used to calculate the Cash Reward.
    Valid entries are:

      D  Daily.  Recalculate the Cash Reward amount daily.
      H  High Amount.  Use the highest calculated reward amount
         for period.
      L  Low Amount.  Use the lowest calculated reward amount
         for period.
                                                                _
    F12=Cancel                                            M01068S

EASEL OFF
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
FIELD=PFKEY,    PIC='X(01)', ATTR=(DISPLAY,HIDDEN)
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
